              <h1 class="signature" translate="no">file(File, Context, Env, Opts)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">Result</span></h1>





          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/edoc/src/edoc_extract.erl#L254" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
