        <div class="specs">
          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Forms = <a href="../../../../lib/syntax_tools/doc/html/erl_syntax.html#t:forms/0">erl_syntax:forms</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">File = <a href="#t:filename/0">filename</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Env = <a href="edoc.html#t:env/0">edoc:env</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Opts = <a href="#t:proplist/0">proplist</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">R = {<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:module/0">module</a>(), <a href="edoc.html#t:edoc_module/0">edoc:edoc_module</a>()} | {<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:module/0">module</a>(), <a href="edoc.html#t:edoc_module/0">edoc:edoc_module</a>(), [<a href="edoc.html#t:entry/0">edoc:entry</a>()]}</pre>

        </div>


<p>Extracts EDoc documentation from commented source code syntax trees. The given <code>Forms</code> must be a single syntax tree of type <code>form_list</code>, or a list of syntax trees representing &quot;program forms&quot; (cf. <a href="edoc.html#read_source/2"><code>edoc:read_source/2</code></a>. <code>Env</code> is an environment created by <a href="edoc_lib.html#get_doc_env/3"><code>edoc_lib:get_doc_env/3</code></a>. The <code>File</code> argument is used for error reporting and output file name generation only.</p><p>See <a href="edoc.html#get_doc/2"><code>edoc:get_doc/2</code></a> for descriptions of the <code>def</code>, <code>hidden</code>, <code>private</code>, and <code>todo</code> options.</p><p><em>See also: </em><a href="../../../../lib/syntax_tools/doc/html/erl_recomment.html">//syntax_tools/erl_recomment</a>, <a href="#source/5">source/5</a>, <a href="edoc.html#read_comments/2">edoc:read_comments/2</a>, <a href="edoc.html#read_source/2">edoc:read_source/2</a>.</p>
  </section>
</section>
<section class="detail" id="source/5">


  <div class="detail-header">
    <a href="#source/5" class="detail-link" data-no-tooltip="" aria-label="Link to this function">
      <i class="ri-link-m" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
