          <h4 class="specs-title">Types</h4>

            <pre translate="no">Text = <a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:string/0">string</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Context = <a href="#t:context/0">context</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Env = <a href="edoc.html#t:env/0">edoc:env</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Opts = <a href="#t:proplist/0">proplist</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Tags = [<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#t:term/0">term</a>()]</pre>

        </div>


<p>Returns the list of tags in the text. Any lines of text before the first tag are ignored. <code>Env</code> is an environment created by <a href="edoc_lib.html#get_doc_env/3"><code>edoc_lib:get_doc_env/3</code></a>.</p><p>See <a href="#source/4"><code>source/4</code></a> for a description of the <code>def</code> option.</p>
  </section>
